OL,3,CWaltham Forest teachers striking over
OL,4,Cpay and school funding
OL,6,FTeachers at a primary school in
OL,7,FWaltham Forest are striking over plans
OL,8,Ffor staff restructuring in a dispute
OL,9,Fover pay and funding.
OL,11,FHenry Maynard Primary School has been
OL,12,Fpraised by Education Secretary Bridget
OL,13,FPhillipson as one of the best schools
OL,14,Fin the country for outcomes for
OL,15,Fdisadvantaged kids. But it is facing
OL,16,Fsevere financial pressures, falling
OL,17,Fpupil numbers and a loss of teachers.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/8
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
