PN,40602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1779228661
OL,3,CWaltham Forest teachers striking over
OL,4,Cpay and school funding
OL,6,FThe teachers striking say the funding
OL,7,Fmodel is not fit for purpose. This has
OL,8,Fled to the school implementing a
OL,9,Frestructure, which in turn has led to
OL,10,Fthe teachers striking.
OL,12,FDaniel Kebede, General Secretary of
OL,13,Fthe National Education Union (NEU),
OL,14,Fsays: "We don't want to see any
OL,15,Fcompulsory redundancies made to staff.
OL,16,FThis leads to bigger class sizes and
OL,17,Fless support, particularly for those
OL,18,Fwith additional special educational
OL,19,Fneeds.
OL,26,@vD@GOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/8
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,407,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1779228661
OL,3,CWaltham Forest teachers striking over
OL,4,Cpay and school funding
OL,6,F"This is happening in schools across
OL,7,FLondon because of a declining pupil
OL,8,Frole. We want this government to take
OL,9,Fnotice and use the declining pupil
OL,10,Frole as an opportunity to bring down
OL,11,Fclass sizes, rather than just close
OL,12,Fschools."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@IO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/8
