CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1779228661
OL,3,CWaltham Forest teachers striking over
OL,4,Cpay and school funding
OL,6,FThe local council - Waltham Forest -
OL,7,Fis classed as an Outer London borough
OL,8,Fin the schools funding model, which
OL,9,Fmeans it receives less money for
OL,10,Feducation from central government than
OL,11,Fan Inner London Borough. However,
OL,12,Fsupporters say this classification no
OL,13,Flonger represents the borough, which
OL,14,Fhas changed significantly since the
OL,15,Ffunding model was designed decades ago.
OL,17,FAs an example, without the Inner
OL,18,FLondon weighting for funding, teachers
OL,19,Fin Waltham Forest could be paid as
OL,20,Fmuch as #6,000 less than neighbouring
OL,21,Fboroughs such as Hackney.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/8
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
