OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,407,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1779228661
OL,3,CWaltham Forest teachers striking over
OL,4,Cpay and school funding
OL,6,FThey say because of the financial
OL,7,Fpressure, the school has been forced
OL,8,Fto implement a restructure
OL,9,F(consultation of what this will look
OL,10,Flike is now underway), and in turn
OL,11,Fteachers have been advised by the NEU
OL,12,Fto stage strike action.
OL,14,FThe strike will span three consecutive
OL,15,Fweeks - the whole of next week, half-
OL,16,Fterm and the whole of the week after
OL,17,Fthat (w/c 1st of June).
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/8
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
