FL,407,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1779228661
OL,3,CWaltham Forest teachers striking over
OL,4,Cpay and school funding
OL,6,FThe strike has strong community
OL,7,Fsupport, with parents saying they love
OL,8,Fthe school and do a lot of fundraising
OL,9,Fto supplement extracurricular
OL,10,Factivities.
OL,12,FHowever, despite supporting the
OL,13,Fstrike, they recognise it will cause
OL,14,Fwidespread disruption. Parents say
OL,15,Fthey are clubbing together and sharing
OL,16,Fchildcare. Some are hosting clubs for
OL,17,Fchildren. There will be limited
OL,18,Fprovision at school for the most
OL,19,Fvulnerable children, and those on Free
OL,20,FSchool Meals.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/8
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
