FL,407,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1779228661
OL,3,CWaltham Forest teachers striking over
OL,4,Cpay and school funding
OL,6,FOne parent, whose son is in reception,
OL,7,Fsays: "The school is already doing a
OL,8,Flot with not a lot of resource so
OL,9,Fanything less than that isn't going to
OL,10,Fbe good enough. Like most parents I
OL,11,Fwork full time, so it's a case of
OL,12,Fjuggling where we can and making sure
OL,13,Fall the parents are pitching in to
OL,14,Fhelp each other. But it's really
OL,15,Fdisruptive to work and life and for
OL,16,Fthem to miss two weeks of school
OL,17,Freally isn't ideal."
OL,26,@oD@GOUyD@TO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G7/8
